\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3887919 RS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9980725\charrsid12015019 Well - when he wasn\rquote 
t working on the estate and it was daylight, he was working in his garden, and my brother and I were working with him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9711576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9980725\charrsid12015019 So really it would }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
