The family together. My brother - brought - what was a phonograph in those days. The round barrel records. Well we had this, and oh I don\rquote t know, we\rquote 
d be about twenty records, it was my brother that really brought it and left it when he went away. And - we used to have these records on. And - very often people landed in and they would put this - phonograph on - to amuse them too.
