t so far away and sometimes - some of those people used to pop in. And I remember - this Mary Cameron. She - little boy, he - he wasn\rquote 
t her boy, she had adopted him. And - they put on the phonograph and it was playing and of course Mary Cameron was - talking away at the same time. And he - wee Willie Murray put his hands - dinna speak Mary, you\rquote ll stop it.
