I can remember - one - he was a Jew used to come round. I think it was more books and things he sold though than - than things to wear, if I remember. What - what\rquote s a colporteur, they used to call them the colporteur. Books. That\rquote 
s right, that\rquote s what they used to call them, the colporteur. Aye, well that\rquote s what he - I think it was more books and traps and things like that that he sold. I don\rquote t remember anybody coming round with - boots and shoes. No, no, that
