A - a - a place where they kept - oil cakes and - and different - feeding stuffs for the - for the cattle. And our place was up above it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9711576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9980725\charrsid12015019 Was it just like an ordinary room in a house?
