Oh no, it was quite comfortable in every way. A good bed. Comfortable bed. And - a wash hand basin. And a jug.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9711576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9980725\charrsid12015019 You didn\rquote t get hot water to wash yourself?
